# ðŸ“¡ streamlit-mgn-metis

Interactive Streamlit tool to enhance coronagraphic images (e.g., METIS) using Multiscale Gaussian Normalization (MGN).

## Features

- Upload FITS image (METIS or similar coronagraph)
- Adjustable **Gamma** parameter
- Optional solar disc masking
- View enhanced output inline
- Download results (**FITS** file + **PNG**) in a ZIP bundle

## Usage

### Local

```bash
git clone https://github.com/gjerse/streamlit-mgn-metis.git
cd streamlit-mgn-metis
pip install -r requirements.txt
streamlit run app.py
